		"description": "Complete collection of all Stakeholder role APIs for PentSecOps Backend\n\nThis collection includes:\n- Authentication (Login)\n- Overview Tab APIs (UC1-UC10)\n- Vulnerabilities Tab APIs (UC11-UC27)\n- Reports Tab APIs (UC28-UC42)\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:8080/api\n\nTest Credentials:\n- Email: stakeholder@test.com\n- Password: stakeholder123",
